u are being shot you have no hope of aiming?  Thats great considering if you move it still doesn't matter.  So, just hit the F9 key and reload!<br><br>4) The enemies have an uncanny knack of being able to &quot;see&quot; you through heavy brush/trees.  Sure you have no chance in hell of seeing them, but expect to be hit by 99% of their shots!<br><br>Sure I could sit here and happily hit the RELOAD key every time I get shot, trying to figure out where the next enemy is that I can't see and then SAVE after I kill him.  That sounds like GREAT fun!<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uanikacrystalwind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Anika Crystalwind</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Admin Gnome</span><br>  Posts: 553<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(1/27/02 4:47:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=800.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://216.122.250.134/html/phnxarmx2.gif width=100 height=102></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: MOH:AA</span><hr size=1> MoH:AA is a lot more fun in multiplayer.  I played the single player campaign just to play it, but the fun are the deathmatch and objective multiplayer - for me at least. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uhrriss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hrriss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(1/27/02 7:54:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReply